subject: Golf
Canadian Open (Golf)
lead_paragraph: Michelle Wie won her second career victory on the L.P.G.A. Tour, shooting a two-under 70 to finish at 12 under for the tournament at the St. Charles Country Club in Winnipeg, Manitoba.
